---
title: Smart Mango Glazed Salmon with Curried Chickpeas and Crispy Shallots
description: Warm your belly and your soul with this hearty salmon dinner! Salmon fillets are topped with mango chutney and roasted until sticky, then paired with a curried chickpea stew! Topped with crispy bits of crunchy shallots, this meal delivers the perfect bite every time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-glace-a-la-mangue-ea59438e.jpg
